author: stefan2
msg: open_path() is a central function in all API calls to FSFS repos, so it
can always use a bit of tuning.  This time, we replace the O(N^2) usage
of svn_fspath__join() with a linear stringbuf traversal.
(open_path): copy path to a stringbuf and simply shift the terminator
position while iterating over the path instead of copying
